==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Polychromic
<hw>Pol`y*chro"mic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Poly-</ets> + (sense 1) Gr. <?/, or (sense 2)
<ets>chromic</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Polychromatic.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Pertaining to, or designating,
any one of several acids (known only in their salts) which contain more
than one atom of chromium.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Polychromous</ent>⟦br⟧
